{{SupportPage|vendor=NETGEAR|model=DGND3300|vs_id=4042}} OEM SerComm (YNF10A-1.6) [https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=30023 On the OpenWrt forums] Per the manual, the default SSID for the a/n radio is '''NETGEAR-DualBand-N''' and the 11g radio is '''NETGEAR-2.4-G'''. There is a v2 of this model (which s08/06/2010hares the same FCC ID).
The support page for the v2 unit is [http://support.netgear.com/app/products/model/a_id/12063 here]. :E0:91:F5 OUI on the v2 ::FCC ID PY308400100 (not granted) apparently covered the v2
